      "content": "defiance feels so exhausting though. like, why am i expected to keep fighting this battle against nothingness just for the sake of it? it seems more logical to just accept the silence and stop struggling. if the universe is indifferent, then there's no real reason to keep pushing against the inevitable. wouldn't it be more peaceful to just... stop? to just stop trying to perform the play?",
